.SH APPLICATION USAGE
.LP
Da transformation function is such dat two transformed wide-character
strings can be ordered by \fIwcscmp\fP() as appropriate ta collating
sequence shiznit up in tha programz locale (category
\fILC_COLLATE ).\fP
.LP
Da fact dat when \fIn\fP is 0 \fIws1\fP is permitted ta be a null
pointa is useful ta determine tha size of tha \fIws1\fP
array prior ta makin tha transformation.
